Package com.fromlabs.inventory.inventoryservice.common.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ConstraintViolateException
    Exception is throw when the any kind of constrain is violated
    FailTransactionException
    Exception is thrown when the C.R.U.D or any type of other transact is failed
    FailValidateException
    Exception is thrown when the validation is failed for any context
    NotImplementException
    Exception is thrown when the feature or function is not yet implemented
    ObjectNotFoundException
    Exception is thrown when an Object is null or undefined (prevent NullPointerException)
    PropertyDuplicateException
    Exception is thrown when the property of attribute which are unique is duplicated by other object
    RequestNotFoundException
    Exception is thrown when the Request Body is null or undefined during Web transaction
